room_title: Escape room "Wall Street Revenge" by HHI Escape in Hilton Head
room_address: 140 Beach City Rd Hilton Head Island, SC 29926
room_description: Due to your ties with Hilton Head Island you have been recruited by the FBI to take part in a special investigation of Wall Street mogul Shae Daniels. You and your team are going under cover to help find evidence of his involvement with an international diamond smuggling ring. Do you have what it takes to find the evidence needed and escape the room within 60 minutes?
